        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> Strike</p>\n<p>Though expensive, these single-use alchemical bombs are often used by police forces to disperse unruly crowds and quell riots without risking permanent physical injury to either officers or civilians.</p>\n<p>The bomb can be thrown up to 30 feet, causing it to explode, spraying the aerosolized pepper dust in a 15-foot-radius burst. All creatures in the area must succeed at a @Check[type:reflex|dc:18|showDC:all] save to avoid inhaling the dust or getting it in their eyes.</p>\n<p>On a failed save, the creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Blinded]{Blinded} for 1 round and then @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dazzled]{Dazzled} for 1 round.</p>\n<p>On a critical failure, the creature is blinded for 1 round, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}, and dazzled until it removes the sickened condition.</p>"
        },
